text_Gabbro: Gabbro has a lack of vertical or horizontal lines. Primarily contain only very small spots. Brown or grey coloring.
text_Pegmatite: Pegmatite has sections that are white, mixed in with other coloring. The lines are mostly at angles, neither horizontal nor vertical.

text_Peridotite: Peridotite has no lines. May contain green coloring that looks like moss.
text_Andesite: Gray, brown or black coloring. White spotting throughout.

text_Basalt: Mostly dark coloring and solid. Lack of lines
text_Diorite: Light coloring. Contains spots of darker coloring.
